                     <interp inst="t18350615-1585-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18350615-cd-187" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18350615-1585-offence-1 t18350615-cd-187"></join>15th of No<lb></lb>vember</rs>, 8 sovereigns, and 13 shillings; the monies of <persName id="t18350615-name-1261" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-1261" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-1261" type="surname" value="READ"></interp>
